12. Nc3 {The Pe4 is in big danger since 12....f5? is refuted by 13.Qb3+.} Bg5
13. Bxg5 Qxg5 14. O-O {Now the lack of development causes Black serious
problems.} f5 15. Qb3+ Rf7 16. d5 $16 {Kuusik,J - Eintalu,J ICCF email 2017})
10. f3 Nd6 11. Qc2 Be6 12. O-O Nd7 13. Kh1 g6 14. g4 $1 Qe8 15. g5 Qd8 16. h4 {
White had a huge space advantage and decent attacking prospects on the k-side
in Degn,B - Hoehne,V LSS email 2018}) 9. O-O h6 {Only this move has an
