10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. Bxe4 dxe4 12. Ng3 f5 {Okamura,M - Gomes,P Rio de Janeiro 2017
} 13. d5 $146 Qe5 14. Qb3 Kh8 15. Rfd1 $36 {White has a serious advantage
