10. Bh4 {Of course, it makes no sense to part with the bishop.} a5 {By making
this move Black prevents the standard ..b2-b4 advance and vacates a6 for his
knight.} ({As earlier, it's better to deviate from active measures such as} 
10... Ne4 11. Bxe7 Qxe7 12. Bxe4 dxe4 13. Ng3 f5 {A sad necessity. Now Black's
king is more exposed.} 14. d5 cxd5 15. Nxd5 $36 {The activity of White's
knights and lack of development make Black's position highly unpleasant.
Anywhere,B - Bongo Akanga Ndjila,B Tornelo INT 2022}) ({Dubious is} 10... Ng4
11. Bg3 $1 {Now the Ng4 is clearly misplaced.} Bd6 12. h3 Nf6 13. Qc2 $14 {
Black was suffering from poor Bc8 in Borkowski,S - Maliszewski,J Polanica
